<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong>What's the difference between web design and graphic design?</strong></h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">While Graphic and <strong>Web Designing Course in Ahmedabad</strong> are both types of visual communication, they're not the same. <strong><a title="Graphic designers" href="https://arenaanimationahmedabad.com/courses/graphics-design">Graphic designers</a></strong> create visual elements like logos, posters and other objects that can be, used in print or online. Web designers focus on creating websites showing how well a business is, organized and how it presents its products or services.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Web designers create websites using technology to build pages that look good and function properly on different devices (such as PCs or mobile phones).</p>
